workhistory.summary: Hey there! As the manager of software engineering at a small company I wore many hats; manager, architect, scrum master, developer. I led and mentored my teams of  professionals to deliver high quality applications on time. Working with all levels of the organization I helped them in defining new, and updates to, application features. And I spent time developing application features.
